description: Luxury living at Echelon Seaport! This stunning 1-bedroom, 1-bath condo offers modern elegance and top-tier amenities in Boston’s vibrant Seaport District. Floor-to-ceiling windows flood the open-concept space with natural light and breathtaking city views. A sleek chef’s kitchen features custom Italian cabinetry, quartz countertops, and premium Thermador appliances. The spacious bedroom includes a walk-in closet, while the spa-inspired bath offers a serene retreat. Enjoy 50,000 sq. ft. of resort-style amenities, including two outdoor pools, an indoor pool, basketball court, golf simulator, fitness center, spa, sky lounge, wine room, and 24/7 concierge. One valet parking space included! Steps from world-class dining, shopping, and entertainment. Motivated seller—don’t miss this opportunity!
